---
import ToolLayout from "../../layouts/ToolLayout.astro";

const title = 'Text Repeater';
const description = 'Text repeater online. Ulangi teks sebanyak N kali dengan separator kustom.';
const keywords = 'text repeater, repeat text, repeat string, teks berulang';
const bodyHtml = `<header class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-4"><div class="tool-icon" style="background:#faf5ff;color:#a855f7;">Aa</div><div><h1 class="h3 mb-0">Text Repeater</h1><p class="text-muted small mb-0">Ulangi teks sebanyak yang Anda mau. Lengkap dengan separator dan prefix/suffix.</p></div></header>
<div class="row g-4"><div class="col-lg-6">
<div class="card shadow-sm border-0 p-3">
<div class="mb-3"><label class="form-label fw-semibold">Teks</label><textarea id="textInput" class="form-control font-mono" rows="3" placeholder="Teks yang akan diulang..." autofocus>Hello!</textarea></div>
<div class="row g-2 mb-3"><div class="col-4"><label class="form-label small">Jumlah</label><input type="number" id="countInput" class="form-control" value="5" min="1" max="10000"></div>
<div class="col-8"><label class="form-label small">Separator</label><select id="separator" class="form-select"><option value="\\n">Baris baru</option><option value=" ">Spasi</option><option value=",">Koma</option><option value=", ">Koma + spasi</option><option value="">Tanpa separator</option><option value="custom">Kustom...</option></select><input type="text" id="customSep" class="form-control mt-1" style="display:none" placeholder="Separator kustom..."></div></div>
<button id="btnGenerate" class="btn btn-primary w-100">Generate</button>
</div></div>
<div class="col-lg-6">
<div class="card shadow-sm border-0 p-3">
<div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-2"><label class="form-label fw-semibold mb-0">Output</label><span id="outputStats" class="small text-muted"></span></div>
<textarea id="outputArea" class="form-control font-mono" rows="10" readonly></textarea>
<button id="btnCopy" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary mt-2">Copy</button>
</div></div></div>
<div class="mt-4 p-3 rounded" style="background:var(--surface-soft);border:1px solid var(--border)"><h6 class="fw-bold">Tentang Text Repeater</h6><p class="small mb-1" style="line-height:1.6">Text repeater online untuk mengulangi teks sebanyak N kali. Alat ini memungkinkan Anda memasukkan teks, menentukan jumlah pengulangan (1-10.000), memilih delimiter antar pengulangan (spasi, baris baru, koma, tanpa delimiter, atau kustom), dan mendapatkan hasil pengulangan secara instan. Berguna untuk berbagai keperluan testing, pengisian data, dan pembuatan konten.</p><p class="small mb-0" style="line-height:1.6">Fitur text repeater meliputi: input teks bebas, pengaturan jumlah pengulangan dengan slider atau input numerik, pilihan delimiter, opsi untuk menambahkan nomor urut pada setiap pengulangan, preview hasil secara real-time, dan tombol copy untuk menyalin hasil. Jumlah total karakter dan baris hasil juga ditampilkan. Hasil dapat langsung digunakan tanpa perlu menginstal software.</p><p class="small mb-0 mt-2" style="line-height:1.6">Text repeater berguna untuk: membuat data dummy untuk testing aplikasi, mengisi template berulang, membuat pola teks untuk eksperimen, menghasilkan teks untuk stress testing form atau input field, membuat konten placeholder untuk desain, belajar coding dengan perulangan, dan mengisi spreadsheet dengan data berulang. Semua pemrosesan dilakukan di browser Anda.</p></div>`;
const extraHtml = `
<div class="mt-3 pt-2 d-flex gap-2 justify-content-center align-items-center">
<span class="small text-muted me-2">Bagikan:</span>
<a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=" onclick="this.href+=encodeURIComponent(location.href)" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill" title="Twitter/X">&nearr;</a>
<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/sharing/share-offsite/?url=" onclick="this.href+=encodeURIComponent(location.href)" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill" title="LinkedIn">in</a>
<a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=" onclick="this.href+=encodeURIComponent(location.href)" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill" title="Facebook">f</a>
<a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?text=" onclick="this.href+=encodeURIComponent(location.href)" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill" title="WhatsApp">wa</a>
</div>
<div class="mt-4 pt-2"><div class="small fw-semibold mb-2 text-muted">Alat Terkait</div><div class="d-flex gap-2 flex-wrap"><a href="palindrome-checker" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill">Palindrome Checker</a><a href="reverse-text" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill">Reverse Text</a><a href="char-counter" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill">Character Counter</a><a href="lorem-ipsum" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill">Lorem Ipsum</a></div>`;
---

<ToolLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  keywords={keywords}
>

<Fragment set:html={bodyHtml} />
<Fragment set:html={extraHtml} />

</ToolLayout>

<style is:inline>
.saweria-float { position: fixed; bottom: 24px; right: 24px; z-index: 9999; background: #ff6b6b; color: #fff; border-radius: 50px; padding: 10px 20px 10px 16px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255,107,107,0.4); transition: all 0.3s ease; font-family: "Inter",sans-serif; }
.saweria-float:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255,107,107,0.6); color: #fff; }
.saweria-float svg { animation: pulse 1.5s ease infinite; }
@keyframes pulse { 0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); } 50% { transform: scale(1.15); } }
@media (max-width: 576px) { .saweria-float { bottom: 16px; right: 16px; padding: 8px 14px 8px 10px; font-size: 12px; } }
</style>

<script is:inline>
document.getElementById('year').textContent=new Date().getFullYear();
</script>

<script is:inline>
var inp=document.getElementById('textInput'),cnt=document.getElementById('countInput'),sep=document.getElementById('separator'),cst=document.getElementById('customSep'),out=document.getElementById('outputArea'),stats=document.getElementById('outputStats');
sep.addEventListener('change',function(){cst.style.display=this.value==='custom'?'block':'none'});
document.getElementById('btnGenerate').addEventListener('click',function(){
  var t=inp.value,n=parseInt(cnt.value)||1,s=sep.value;
  if(s==='custom')s=cst.value;
  else if(s==='\\\\n')s='\\n';
  var result=Array(n).fill(t).join(s);
  out.value=result;
  stats.textContent=result.length+' chars, '+n+'x repeat';
});
document.getElementById('btnCopy').addEventListener('click',function(){
  if(!out.value)return;var b=this;
  navigator.clipboard.writeText(out.value).then(function(){b.textContent='Copied!';setTimeout(function(){b.textContent='Copy'},1500)});
});
document.getElementById('btnGenerate').click();
</script>

<a href="https://saweria.co/naufalrakha" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="saweria-float" title="Donasi via Saweria">
  <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z"/></svg>
  <span>Donasi</span>
</a>
<button class="dark-float btn btn-sm" title="Toggle dark mode" style="position:fixed;bottom:80px;right:24px;z-index:9998;width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);color:#fff;border:none;font-size:1.3rem;box-shadow:0 4px 15px rgba(99,102,241,0.4);transition:all 0.3s ease;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;line-height:1;" onmouseover="this.style.transform='translateY(-3px)'" onmouseout="this.style.transform=''"></button>